## Infrastructure Topology

```
GitHub  →  Render (FastAPI API)  →  Upstash Redis  →  Render (Worker)
                ↓                                           ↓
           Neon Postgres + pgvector              Google AI (Gemini 2.5 Flash)
                ↓                                           ↓
           Langfuse Cloud (tracing)                  Langfuse Cloud (tracing)

Vercel (React SPA)  →  Render (FastAPI API)
```

### Environment Separation
- `development`: Docker Compose (local Postgres + Redis)
- `staging`: Render preview deploys, Neon branch DB
- `production`: Render web service + worker, Neon main DB, Upstash production

