## API Versioning

All routes prefixed `/api/v1/`. Breaking changes increment to `/api/v2/` with a deprecation period.

| Route | Method | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `/api/v1/webhooks/github` | POST | GitHub App event receiver |
| `/api/v1/auth/github` | GET | Redirect to GitHub OAuth |
| `/api/v1/auth/callback` | GET | OAuth callback, issue session JWT |
| `/api/v1/repos` | GET | List installed repos for current user |
| `/api/v1/repos/{id}/config` | GET / PATCH | Read / update agent config for a repo |
| `/api/v1/reviews` | GET | Paginated reviews (filter by repo) |
| `/api/v1/reviews/{id}` | GET | Single review with full findings |
| `/api/v1/jobs/{id}` | GET | Review job status |

